								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">1/ 咨询专业的法律顾问，审核现有的</span><strong><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(214, 168, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">“商场统一销售合同”</span></strong
									><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">以及与商户的租赁合同，研究《消费者权益保护法》等相关的法律条文，理清销售合同以及租赁合同中相关条款内容涉及的法律责任是否清晰明确。</span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">2/ 检查卖场内商户的质量保证金和履约保证金是否正常缴纳。</span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">3/ 尽可能地要求商户与消费者采用商场的统一订单，尽可能要求统一收银；</span
									><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(214, 168, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><strong>因为即使不走商场的订单和统一收银，商场也得承担相应责任。</strong></span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">4/ 对商户的经营情况、老板的个人情况尽可能摸排清楚，判断其资金情况，是否具备持续经营的能力？资金链能保证店铺正常经营多久。与其被动等问题发生，不如主动去预防和规避问题产生。</span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">5/ 对商户的营销政策密切关注，商户采取明显低于正常成交价或者成本价销售产品，同时又引导消费者交全款的情况，商场必须介入。</span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">6/ 积极为商户引入金融服务支持，鼓励商户走正常渠道贷款，缓解资金压力。</span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">7/ 商场运营和客服做好每一个商户与消费者成交的订单跟踪</span><span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">（包括还未送货的历史订单）</span
