								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">商户与消费者的交易是订货制，消费者先付定金甚至是全款，然后商户才向工厂下订单。而商户与工厂也是订货制，商户必须先交钱，工厂才发货，所以商户的逃场问题很难从根本上规避。</span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important"><br /></span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">据了解，有个别家居卖场采取了类似支付宝的模式，100%统一收银，所有的消费者货款都是由商场代收，消费者收到货之后，商场才给商户返款，这样就能有效避免商户逃场的问题。</span>
								</section>
								<section style="margin: 0em 32px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important">
									<span style="font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.544px"><br /></span>
								</section>
